title: Howard Stern-Booey 100 (2016 Edition)
description:
Booey 100 (2016 Edition)

Some differences between this & last years Booey 100 that I noticed, while skipping through some of both are.

* All Casey Kasem bits have been removed.
* All special VJ host segments removed.
* All Bumpers, Sweepers, Stingers and Drops updated.

* Added special guest shout outs.

* 2015 was 2 parts at just over 6hrs each.
* 2016 is 7 parts at 3hrs+ each.

There are probably more & I would've loved to provide a setlist but that would take a lot of time & work to search out what songs are being parodied. 


One other thing is that a lot of songs seem to be used multiple times
